@startuml
title BP-12 - Discount Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Create discount rule;
:Select applicable product or billing period;
:Define amount, percentage or early payment rule;

|Platform|
:Validate tenant scope;
:Validate discount value;
:Validate conflict with scholarship or existing rule;

if (Discount valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save discount configuration;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Billing Engine|
:Apply discount before obligation finalization;
:Record discount as adjustment metadata;

|Parent Guardian|
:View reduced payable amount;
stop

note right
Current MVP code does not yet implement a dedicated discount module.
Use this as future business process documentation.
end note
@enduml
